#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Cooking with Maths*"
msgstr "*用数学烹饪*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Cooking can help your child start learning maths!"
msgstr "烹饪可以帮助你的孩子开始学习数学！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💚 Invite your child to help you cook for your family, or to choose something they would like to cook"
msgstr "💚 邀请你的孩子帮你给家人做饭，或者烹饪他们想做的其他东西"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🍅 Ask your child to count different ingredients. Help them if it’s difficult!"
msgstr "🍅 让你的孩子数一数食材各有几个。如果孩子遇到困难，帮帮他们！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔟 Help your child to understand adding and subtracting quantities "
msgstr "🔟 帮助你的孩子理解加法和减法 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 Encourage your child to recognise numbers on packaging"
msgstr "📝 鼓励你的孩子认出食品包装上的数字"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid " 👀 Ask your child about the different sizes of ingredients - e.g. which is bigger/biggest?"
msgstr " 👀 问问你的孩子不同食材的大小 - 比如，这些食材哪个比较大/最大？"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Think about when you will cook together again! You can also practise understanding numbers and quantities during other activities like shopping or building/making things"
msgstr "🔄 想想之后什么时候再跟孩子一起做饭！你也可以在其他活动中让孩子练习理解数字和数量，比如去购物或搭积木/做手工的时候"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Following Instructions*"
msgstr "*听从指令*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 Play a game in which your child listens to and tries to remember strings of instructions."
msgstr "👂 跟你的孩子玩一个游戏，在游戏中孩子必须听从并尝试记住你的一串指令。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This will be useful in school, at home, and later in life!"
msgstr "这会对孩子在学校、在家和以后的生活都有所帮助！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Start with just one instruction using an object in your home. For example “touch the red ball” 🔴"
msgstr "从只给出一个指令开始，选择家里的一样物品。比如“触碰那个红色的球”。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Slowly add more instructions (e.g “then pick up the cup ☕), but tell your child that they can only start once you’ve finished giving the instructions."
msgstr "逐渐增加更多指令（比如“然后，拿起杯子☕”），但告诉你的孩子只有在你说完所有指令之后才能开始行动。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "See how many your child can follow without forgetting!"
msgstr "看看你的孩子能够记住并且执行多少指令不会忘！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Now swap roles! It’s your child’s turn to give you instructions! They can use the same objects if they want."
msgstr "🔄 现在角色互换！轮到你的孩子给你指令了！如果愿意的话，他们也可以使用同样的物品。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "You can also try this game with a group of children! Make sure they take turns :)"
msgstr "你还可以尝试和几个孩子一起玩这个游戏！确保他们都能轮流玩到游戏 :)"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*One-on-One Time*"
msgstr "“一对一时光”"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💚 Spending time just with your child and taking an interest in them can improve your relationship"
msgstr "💚 与孩子单独共度时光并且关注他们，可以改善你们的关系。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 When you child is playing alone or occupying themselves quietly, join them and show interest in what they are doing"
msgstr "👀 当你的孩子独自玩耍或安静地自娱自乐时，你可以加入他们并且对他们正在做的事情表露出兴趣。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂Ask questions about their activity, and listen to them"
msgstr "👂 询问他们正在做的事情，并且听他们回答"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let your child lead the activity, follow them to build their confidence and autonomy 😃"
msgstr "让你的孩子主导活动并且听从他们，这样能够帮助他们建立自信心和自主性 😃"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Say what you see - describing everything and supporting your child’s actions"
msgstr "👀 说出你所看到的 - 描述你看到的所有东西，并且支持你孩子的做为"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Be positive, praise your child, and enjoy spending this time with them 😃💚"
msgstr "保持积极，乐于赞美你的孩子，并且享受和他们共度时光 😃💚"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Playtime with Books*"
msgstr "*边读边玩*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📖 Book sharing will help your child learn and is a fun, playful activity to spend quality time together"
msgstr "📖 陪孩子一起读书有助于他们学习知识，而且这是一项好玩的、充满乐趣的活动，可以让你和孩子一起度过高质量的亲子时光"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏰ Choose a time when you won’t be disturbed, and try to stop any distractions - e.g. turn off the TV and put away phones"
msgstr "⏰ 选择一个不会有人打扰的时间，并尽量杜绝任何会让你们分心的东西 - 比如关掉电视并且放下手机"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📖 If your child wants to choose a book, that’s fine, otherwise choose for them"
msgstr "📖 如果你的孩子想选一本书，那再好不过，不然你也可以帮他们选择一本"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💚 Sit close together and follow your child attention and lead "
msgstr "💚 和你的孩子挨着坐，并且跟随孩子的注意力和主导 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Point at things, name and repeat words. Help your child learn more about what interests them in the book 👀 "
msgstr "指着书上的事物说出相应的名称，多重复几遍。帮助你的孩子多了解书中他们感兴趣的内容 👀 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "If there are words or numbers in the book, ask and help your child recognise numbers and simple words 💡 "
msgstr "如果书上有汉字或数字，可以向你的孩子提问，并帮孩子认识数字和简单的字词 💡 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Link things in the books to your child life, and use words about emotions and talk about them! 😃"
msgstr "将书上的事物与你孩子的生活联系起来，可以使用表达情绪的词汇来描述它们！ 😃"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 If possible, start a regular routine to read together when your child isn’t too tired or hungry"
msgstr "🔄 如果可能的话，尽量让你的孩子养成在他还不太累或饿的时候开始一起读书的惯例"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Reading together is one of the best ways to help your child learn and prepare for success in school! 🎓"
msgstr "一起读书是让你的孩子学习知识和为取得学业成绩做准备的最好方法之一！ 🎓"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Link things in the books to your child's life, and use words about emotions and talk about them! 😃"
msgstr "将书上的事物与你孩子的生活联系起来，可以使用表达情绪的词汇来描述它们！ 😃"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*I Spy!*"
msgstr "*我是间谍！*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 I spy is a fun game to play with your child that will help them learn about pinyin!"
msgstr "👀 “我是间谍”是一个可以和孩子一起玩的有趣游戏，可以有效帮助他们学习拼音！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Choose an object or a thing around you, and don’t tell your child what it is. It should be something that your child knows the word for. For example “ball” ⚽"
msgstr "选择一个你周围的物品或事物，不要告诉你的孩子你选的是什么。这个东西应该是一个你的孩子知道名称的东西，比如“球”⚽"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Then say “I spy with my little eye, something beginning with *and then say the shengmu* which in this case is “q”"
msgstr "👀 然后说”小眼睛，找一找，谁的声母是......（在“球”的例子中应该说‘q’）“"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Your child should look around and guess what the object is. When they guess it right, praise them and swap roles! If they can’t get it, give them some clues, like “it’s round” or “it’s black and white”. ✅"
msgstr "这时你的孩子应该看看周围，猜测你选的东西是什么。当他们猜对时，夸奖他们，并且和他们交换角色！如果猜不出来，给他们一些线索，比如“它是圆的”或者“它是黑白相间的”。 ✅"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Play this game with as many objects as possible and as many different ciyu! Help your child to learn about the different wordsand sounds . This will help them learn to read at home and school. 🎓"
msgstr "尽量选择不同物品和词语来玩这个游戏，越多越好！让你的孩子认识不同的词汇和声音，这将有助于他们在家和学校学会如何阅读。 🎓"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Categorising and Organising*"
msgstr "* 分类和归纳*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Help your child to learn by sorting objects and things! 🔵🔷"
msgstr "让你的孩子从将物品和事物归类中学习！🔵🔷"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Your child will learn by understanding how things fit and group together (eg, bear = animal"
msgstr "你的孩子可以通过理解如何将事物归类和分组来学习（例如，熊=动物，"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "mango = fruit, blue = colour) 🧸"
msgstr "芒果=水果，蓝色=颜色）🧸"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Find a book with different pictures and help your child to find things in a particular category (e.g. “Find all of the animals”) 👀"
msgstr "找一本有很多插图的书，然后让你的孩子在书中寻找某个特定类别的物品（比如“找到所有动物”）👀"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Find safe objects in the house, get your child to group them by colour, size, or types of object (potatoes, cucumbers). Then make more complicated categories (e.g. small potatoes, big potatoes) 🥔"
msgstr "在家里寻找没有危险性的物品，并且让你的孩子把它们按照颜色、大小或物品类别（比如土豆、黄瓜）分组，然后再按照更复杂的类别分组（比如小土豆、大土豆）🥔"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 You can play the categorising game anywhere! Just look around and ask your child to find things from the category you say!"
msgstr "🔄 你们可以在任何地方玩这个分类游戏！你只需要看看四周，让你的孩子寻找你说出的类别的物品！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*What Wordis This?*"
msgstr "”这是什么字？“"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Playing games with pinyincan help your child learn how shengmu and yunmuare put together to make the sound of a character."
msgstr "和孩子一起玩拼音游戏可以帮助他们学习声母和韵母如何组合成一个汉字的发音。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 Write a shengmuon a piece of card or paper (e.g. “p”)"
msgstr "📝 在卡片或纸上写下一个声母（比如“p”）"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 Say the shengmuout loud and ask your child to say it too!"
msgstr "👂 大声念出这个声母，让你的孩子跟着你一起读！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Ask your child to say some words that begin with the shengmu“p”, give them clues like “What starts with “p”? Paopao… what else? 🌱"
msgstr "让你的孩子说几个声母是“p”的汉字，给他们一些提示，比如“声母是‘p’的字有哪些？泡泡...... 还有什么？”🌱"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Ask your child to look for objects in your house that begin with a shengmu(eg “b” for beizi). Help them find things."
msgstr "👀 让你的孩子在家里寻找含有某个声母的物品（比如“b”可以找到“杯子”）。引导他们找到相应的物品。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Try a new shengmu or yunmuevery day!"
msgstr "🔄 每天尝试一个新的声母或韵母！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Riddles Help Children Learn*"
msgstr "*益智谜语*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Riddles and puzzles are a fun way to build thinking skills! 💡"
msgstr "谜语和拼图是培养孩子思维能力的有趣方式！💡"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Do you remember any riddles from your childhood? If you can’t then make one up, they can be very simple! 😃"
msgstr "你还记得小时候的谜语吗？如果不记得，那就现编一个，非常简单的谜语也可以！😃"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Like “What can you see at night but not in the day” Answer: “The moon” 🌙"
msgstr "比如“什么东西晚上能看到，但白天看不到” 答案是：“月亮” 🌙"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "If your child is finding them difficult, try an easy one like: “What is round, bouncy and can be thrown or kicked?” Answer: “A ball” ⚽"
msgstr "如果你的孩子觉得太难了，换一个更简单的谜语试试，比如：“什么东西圆圆的，有弹性，可以被扔来扔去或者踢来踢去？” 答案是：“球”⚽"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Your child can also try making riddles! 💡"
msgstr "你的孩子也可以试着编写谜语！💡"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "You can have fun with riddles anywhere at any time - like travelling on a bus or in a car 🚗"
msgstr "你们可以随时随地玩谜语游戏 - 比如在坐公交车或者汽车的时候🚗"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*What's New?*"
msgstr "*点亮新技能*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Learning is fun! 🎓"
msgstr "学习是有乐趣的！🎓"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "❓ Ask your child to think of a new, fun thing you could learn together. "
msgstr "❓ 让您的孩子想出一件可以一起学习的新的、有趣的事情。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "For example: keeping a ball in the air with your foot, juggling, cooking rice, tiaofangzi, whistling, learning all the provinces in China. "
msgstr "例如：用脚颠球、耍杂技、蒸米饭、跳房子、吹口哨、学习中国的所有省份等。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Take turns trying out the new thing. Make sure to praise each other and learn and play together!"
msgstr "🔄 轮流去尝试新的东西。要和孩子相互夸奖，一起在玩中学！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💛 Approach learning the thing in a kind and fun way, and do not judge your child or yourself for your ability in the process. "
msgstr "💛 对学习这件事抱持一种友善、轻松的方式，在这个过程中不要去评价孩子或者你自己的能力。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 Once you have mastered the new thing, choose another thing to learn together."
msgstr "😃 一旦你们掌握了一项新事物，就再选择另一个一起开始学习。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Make up a Story*"
msgstr "*编故事*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Creating stories together is a great way to have fun with imagination - and to build your child’s creativity! 📖"
msgstr "和孩子一起创作故事是让你的孩子发挥想象力和培养创造力的好方法！📖"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "5️⃣ With your child, come up with 5 words to use. They can be any words you want! For example: banana, spaceship, fish, water, painting, cooking, wedding. If you need to remember them, write them clearly on a paper with your child."
msgstr "5️⃣ 和你的孩子一起想出5个词语。它们可以是任何你们想要的词语！比如：香蕉，宇宙飞船，鱼，水，画画，烹饪，婚礼。如果你们记不住这些词，可以和孩子一起在纸上清晰地写下来。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎂 Start your story with, “Once upon a time, there was a…” and use one of the words from the list in the first part. For example, “Once upon a time, there was a family who worked on a *banana* farm.”"
msgstr "🎂 让你们的故事以“从前，有一个…”开头，然后用出你们词汇表中的一个词语。比如，“从前，有一家人以种*香蕉*为生。”"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 Let your child make up the next part using another word from the list."
msgstr "📝 让你的孩子用词汇表中的另一个词语编出故事的下一部分。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Take turns until you have used all the words and created a story. "
msgstr "🔄 和孩子轮流进行，直到你们用上了所有词语编出了一个故事。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔔 Be creative and do not tell your child what to say. It does not need to be a real story to be fun!"
msgstr "🔔 保持创造力，不要教你的孩子应该说什么。故事不一定要是真实的，只要有趣就行！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎁 Ask your child what their favourite part of the story was, and tell them yours!"
msgstr "🎁 问问你的孩子他们最喜欢故事的哪个部分，然后告诉他们你最喜欢的部分！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Playing with Clothes*"
msgstr "*衣服游戏*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡Help your child use their fingers, talk about clothes, and organise them! "
msgstr "💡让你的孩子动动手指，跟他们讲讲衣服，并且让他们试着把衣服整理好！ "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Help your child exercise their fingers by showing them how buttons and zips work on clothes, and letting them practise using them! 👋"
msgstr "给你的孩子展示衣服上纽扣和拉链的工作原理，并且让他们练习扣扣子和拉拉链，这样可以帮助孩子锻炼手指的灵活性！👋"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔵 Talk about the colours of clothes! Ask your child to pick a colour and talk about all the things that are that colour: “What are all the things we can think of that are blue?”"
msgstr "🔵 和孩子聊聊衣服的颜色！让你的孩子选择一种颜色，并且说出所有拥有这种颜色的物品：“我们能想到都有哪些东西是蓝色的？”"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 Encourage your child to help you sort clothes into piles for each family member."
msgstr "😃 鼓励你的孩子帮你把衣服按照属于不同家庭成员分类并且叠成摞。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Playing with Vegetables*"
msgstr "*蔬菜游戏*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🌱 Help your child learn by thinking and talking about vegetables!"
msgstr "🌱 帮助你的孩子在思考和谈论蔬菜中学习！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🍅 Mix together 2-3 different ingredients of your choice (like onions, tomatoes and corn example). Say: “Help me sort these vegetables into piles?” Try sorting them by size."
msgstr "🍅 把2-3种不同的食材混合起来（比如洋葱、番茄和玉米）。然后说：“能帮我把这些蔬菜分类吗？”尝试让孩子按照大小分类。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 Remind me!"
msgstr "😃 记住！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Talk about your child’s experiences. Ask questions and wait for answers. Follow your child’s interest. "
msgstr "讲讲你的孩子的体验。问他们问题并且等待他们的回答。跟随你孩子的兴趣。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "“Can you help me remember what is at the market?” “Do they sell carrots at the market?” “Do the sell anything yellow at the market?” “What else do they sell?” “Can you think of other things they sell?”"
msgstr "“你能帮我回想一下，超市里都卖什么吗？”“那里有卖胡萝卜的吗？”“那里有卖什么黄色的东西吗？”“那里还卖什么其他的吗？”“你还能想到他们卖什么别的吗？”"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡Can you think of something similar?"
msgstr "💡 你能想到什么类似的东西吗？"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Say: We are going to think of some things that are similar or different from what I tell you. So listen carefully!”"
msgstr "你可以说：“我们现在要想一些别的东西，它可能和我告诉你的东西类似，或者和我告诉你的东西不同。所以听好了！”"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Here is a tomato. Can you think of something else that is red like a tomato? 🍅"
msgstr "这里有一个番茄。你能想到其他什么东西，和番茄一样是红色的吗？🍅"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Can you think something else that is round like a tomato? ⚽"
msgstr "你能想到其他什么东西，和番茄一样是圆的吗？⚽"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Animals*"
msgstr "*动物*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🧸 Active animals: Take turns with your child doing animal actions: Hop like a frog, stretch like a cat, run like a dog, slither like a snake, flap like a bird"
msgstr "🧸 活泼的小动物：和你的孩子轮流模仿动物做动作：像青蛙一样跳，像猫一样伸懒腰，像狗一样奔跑，像蛇一样滑行，像鸟一样拍打翅膀"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡All the animals we can think of - think about groups of animals!"
msgstr "💡 我们能想到哪些动物 - 想想一群动物！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "What are all the animals we can think of that have feathers?"
msgstr "我们能想到哪些有羽毛的动物？"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "What are all the animals we can think of that eat plants? 🌱"
msgstr "我们能想到哪些吃草的动物？🌱"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "What are all the animals we can think of that lay eggs?"
msgstr "我们能想到哪些产卵的动物？"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 Counting rabbits"
msgstr "😃 数兔子"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔟 Find 10 rocks and put them in a line, tell your child that they are rabbits!"
msgstr "🔟 找到10块石头，把它们排成一排。告诉你的孩子，它们是小兔子！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Ask your child to count the rabbits!"
msgstr "让你的孩子数数有多少只小兔子！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Put the rabbits into 2 equal piles. Ask your child to give you 3 rabbits. Say “If you give me 3, how many rabbits do you have”"
msgstr "把所有兔子分成相同的两堆。让你的孩子给你3只兔子，然后说：“如果你给我3只，现在你还剩下多少只兔子？”"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Active Counting*"
msgstr "*边动边数*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👋 Clap, hop, jump: Play the following game with your child. Make it active!"
msgstr "👋 拍手，单脚跳，双脚跳：试着和你的孩子一起玩接下来游戏。动起来！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1️⃣ Clap hands 1 time. 2️⃣ Clap hands 2 times."
msgstr "1️⃣ 拍1次手。 2️⃣ 拍2次手。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1️⃣ Jump 1 time. 2️⃣ Jump 2 times."
msgstr "1️⃣ 双脚跳1次。 2️⃣ 双脚跳2次。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1️⃣ Hop 1 time."
msgstr "1️⃣ 单脚跳1次。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3️⃣ Hop 3 times."
msgstr "1️⃣ 单脚跳3次。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡Can you hop, then jump, then clap? "
msgstr "💡你能先单脚跳1次，然后双脚跳1次，最后拍1次手吗？ "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🏆 Can you clap twice, jump once, and hop three times?"
msgstr "🏆 你能先拍2次手，然后双脚跳1次，最后单脚跳3次吗？"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡Remembering Instructions"
msgstr "💡记住指令动作"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Take turns playing a game where you give 2-3 instructions that the other person has to remember to follow. Make sure physical movement is included!"
msgstr "你可以和孩子轮流玩这个游戏：一方给另一方2-3个指令动作，另一方必须记住并遵循这些指令。记住指令里一定要包含身体动作！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "For example:"
msgstr "比如："

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Hop twice, turn around."
msgstr "单脚跳2次，转一圈。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Jump to the kitchen, pick up a spoon, then run back. ✅"
msgstr "双脚跳到厨房，拿一把勺子，然后跑回来。✅"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Thinking Games*"
msgstr "*思维游戏*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "❗ Mama/Daddy says! Play this game of giving instructions:"
msgstr "❗ 妈妈/爸爸说！你可以和孩子玩下面这个给出指令的游戏："

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Mama/daddy says touch your head. Mama/daddy says open your mouth. Mama/daddy says turn around. Mama/daddy says touch your knees. Mama/daddy says jump twice. Mama/daddy says jump, then clap and sit."
msgstr "妈妈/爸爸说，摸摸你的头。妈妈/爸爸说，张开你的嘴。妈妈/爸爸说，转个圈。妈妈/爸爸说，摸摸你的膝盖。妈妈/爸爸说，双脚跳2次。妈妈/爸爸说，双脚跳1次，拍1次手，然后坐下。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 Go and stop: Play the game with your child"
msgstr "👂 一二三，木头人：和你的孩子一起试试这个游戏"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Say: When I say “stop”, we freeze. When I say “go”, we can walk again."
msgstr "跟孩子说：“当我说‘木头人’的时候，我们就要变成不能动的木头人。当我说‘一二三’的时候，我们可以继续开始走路。”"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Once your child is familiar with the game, your child will lead."
msgstr "一旦你的孩子熟悉了这个游戏，就让他们试着主导这个游戏。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔵 🔴Blue-Red - now play this game!"
msgstr "🔵 🔴蓝色和红色 - 现在再来玩这个游戏试试看！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "If I say touch something blue, you need to touch something red. If I say touch something red, you need to touch something blue."
msgstr "如果我说摸蓝色的东西，你就得摸红色的东西。如果我说摸红色的东西，你就得摸蓝色的东西。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Games with Pictures!*"
msgstr "*图片游戏！*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 Making up a story from an image"
msgstr "👂 从一张图片出发编故事"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "For example, say: We are going to make up a story about this picture. I can start. This little girl is feeling very excited today. Why do you think she is feeling excited?"
msgstr "比如你说：我们现在要看着这张图片编一个故事。我可以先来。这个小女孩今天感觉特别兴奋。你认为她为什么感觉很兴奋呢？"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 She is holding her bag and has a big smile. Where do you think she is going?"
msgstr "😃 她拿着她的包，笑容很灿烂。你觉得她要去哪呢？"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Can you point to it?"
msgstr "👀 你能指出它是什么吗？"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Using a book or a magazine, or anything with pictures, say:"
msgstr "找一本书、杂志或任何其他带有图片的东西，然后说："

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "I am going to describe something on the page and you need to guess what it is and point to it. For example, “I see something that is [green and moves slowly]."
msgstr "我现在要描述这张纸上的某个东西，你需要猜出我说的是什么并且指出它。比如，“我看到一个东西，它是[绿色的，并且移动得很缓慢]。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Can you guess what it is?” 💚"
msgstr "你能猜出它是什么吗？”💚"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Shapes Everywhere!*"
msgstr "*无处不在的形状！*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📺 Squares, squares everywhere"
msgstr "📺 正方形，到处都是正方形"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Draw squares in the sand,  dirt, or on paper. Make some bigger and some smaller."
msgstr "👀 在沙子、土地或者纸上画几个正方形。画一些大的和一些小的。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Tell your child, “this is a square.” "
msgstr "告诉你的孩子：“这是一个正方形。” "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Ask your child to try to draw a square. Hold your child’s hand to help if this is hard. "
msgstr "让你的孩子试着画一个正方形。如果这对孩子来说比较难，你可以握住孩子的手帮着一起画。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Look for things around the home or outdoors that are the same shape."
msgstr "在家里或室外找找其他具有相同形状的物品。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Now do the same with circles! 🔴"
msgstr "现在试着换成圆形做和上面一样的事情！🔴"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Story Telling*"
msgstr "*讲故事*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 Let’s make a story!"
msgstr "💡 让我们一起来编一个故事！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Say: We are going to make up a story. I will start then you will help me continue it. "
msgstr "跟孩子说：“我们现在要编一个故事。我先开始，然后你来帮我继续往下编。” "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏰ ”Once upon a time there was…”"
msgstr "⏰ “从前，有一个…”"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "“What happened next?”"
msgstr "“接下来发生了什么？”"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "“What happened after that?”"
msgstr "“在那之后又发生了什么呢？”"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 Tell me the story!"
msgstr "👂 给我讲讲那个故事吧！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Say to your child: “I have a book here that we have read before. Can you remember the story and tell it to me just by looking at the pictures?” "
msgstr "对你的孩子说：“我这里有一本我们以前读过的书。光看图片，你能记起书里的故事并且讲给我听吗？” "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Show your child pictures in the book. Ask your child what is happening in the pictures and what happens next."
msgstr "👀 把书中的图片展示给你的孩子。问问孩子图片中正在发生什么，以及接下来会发生什么。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*I'm a Writer!*"
msgstr "*我是小作家！*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 Have fun being creative with writing!"
msgstr "📝 享受充满创造力的写字的乐趣！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "You and your child can have fun writing with a pencil and paper, or with a stick and the sand!"
msgstr "你和你的孩子可以用铅笔在纸上写，也可以用木棍在沙子上写着玩！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "If your child doesn’t know how to write characters, encourage them to draw shapes, and try to copy the shapes of characters. 🔵▶️"
msgstr "如果你的孩子还不知道怎么写汉字，那就鼓励他们画画图形，并且试着模仿汉字的形状。🔵▶️"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "When they are more confident, encourage them to write simple characters. 😃"
msgstr "当他们更有信心时，你可以鼓励他们开始写简单的汉字。😃"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Show them the simple things that you write - like shopping lists! Show them the characters they may know. Let them try to copy the characters! 📖"
msgstr "向他们展示你写的简单的东西 - 比如购物清单！向他们展示他们可能认识的汉字。让他们尝试仿写这些汉字！📖"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*A Friendly Chat*"
msgstr "*友好的聊天*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Talk to your child about something that they are interested in! 😃"
msgstr "多和你的孩子聊聊他们感兴趣的事情！😃"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💚 Spending quality time with your child and talking to them every day is a good way to develop a strong relationship. "
msgstr "💚 和你的孩子共度高质量的亲子时光并且每天都和他们交流，是一个建立稳固的亲子关系的好方法。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⚽ An easy way to start talking to your child is to ask them about something they are interested in, for example you could talk about topics such as: sports, books, movies, friends, music, celebrities, or school."
msgstr "⚽ 和孩子开启聊天的一个简单方法是问问他们感兴趣的事情，比如，你可以跟他们聊聊这些主题：体育、书籍、电影、朋友、音乐、名人或者学校。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 You may not find everything your child shares to be interesting, but it’s important to show enthusiasm and an eagerness to learn."
msgstr "👂 可能并不是你的孩子分享的所有内容都很有趣，但是你表现出想要多了解的热情和渴望非常重要。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Get Active*"
msgstr "*动起来！*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Exercise is a great way to spend time together and it is so good for your health. 🌱 Find a sport or exercise that both you and your child want to do and try it out together! "
msgstr "锻炼是一种让你和孩子一起共度时光的好方法，而且对你们的健康也非常有益。🌱 找到一种你和你的孩子都想做的运动或锻炼方式，一起试试吧！ "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏰ Even walking for 10 minutes a day is good for you. "
msgstr "⏰ 即使只是每天一起散步10分钟也对你们很有好处。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⚽ Together you can walk, run, play soccer, swim, dance, or do any other sport.."
msgstr "⚽ 你们可以一起散步、跑步、踢足球、游泳、跳舞或者做任何其他运动。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🏆 Together, think of ways to make it even more fun. Can you jog to a certain point? Take turns being the coach? Can there be a small, free reward, like getting to decide the next activity?"
msgstr "🏆 一起想办法，让运动变得更有趣。你们可以跑到某个特定的终点吗？或者轮流当教练？或许可以为赢家设置一个小小的奖励，比如有权决定下一个活动是什么？"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🌈 Exercise becomes easier and more enjoyable the more you do it. "
msgstr "🌈 运动得越频繁，往往就会变得越容易，也越愉快。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 If you or your child do not like the first exercise you pick, try a new exercise."
msgstr "🔄 如果你或你的孩子不喜欢你选择的第一项运动，换个别的运动试试。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Pass the Ball*"
msgstr "*传球*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Games are a great, fun way to spend time with your family! "
msgstr "一起玩游戏是一个和家人共度时光的有意思的好方法！ "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3️⃣ This game is best with at least 3 people."
msgstr "3️⃣ 下面这个游戏需要至少3个人。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⚽ Find a ball to play. If you cannot find a ball, choose an item you can safely throw around. For example, a bottle cap or a plastic cup."
msgstr "⚽ 找一个球来玩。如果你们找不到球，选择一个可以安全地扔来扔去的物品。比如，瓶盖或塑料杯子。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "➡️ Start in a circle and pass the ball around. "
msgstr "➡️ 从一个起点开始把球传到周围。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👋 Start throwing the ball in new directions (up, down, straight, curved, rolling on the ground) and with different forces (hard, soft, medium). You can bounce the ball, throw it in the air, and catch it a few times before passing it. "
msgstr "👋 可以试着把球扔向不同的方向（往上，往下，直线，曲线，在地上滚动），或者用不同的力量扔出（重重地，轻轻地，不轻不重地）。在传球之前，你可以把球在地上弹几下，或者抛到空中接住几次。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✨ When everyone gets good at catching the ball, you can start moving around the room, still passing the ball. "
msgstr "✨ 当每个人都能熟练地接到球之后，你们可以开始一边在房间里四处走动，一边传球。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ Can you throw the ball under the leg? Behind the back? Over your head? Block a pass? Have fun with it!"
msgstr "⭐ 你能把球从腿下面、从背后、从头顶传出去吗？或者试试阻碍别人的传球？玩得开心！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Active Songs*"
msgstr "*边唱边动*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 Young children love physical games! But they need reminders about how to play 💡"
msgstr "😃 年纪小的孩子喜欢运动游戏！但是需要有人提醒他们怎么玩 💡"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎵 Songs with movements are fun and active and give instructions on how to move!"
msgstr "🎵 带有动作的歌曲是很好玩的，可以让他们动起来，还能指导他们怎么做动作！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Sing songs to your child or a group of children in which they have to:"
msgstr "你可以对你的孩子或者一群孩子唱歌。在你唱歌时，他们必须："

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Start ✅ and stop ❌"
msgstr "开始 ✅ 和停止 ❌"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Slow down ⬇️ and speed up ⬆️"
msgstr "减速 ⬇️ 和加速 ⬆️"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Follow the Leader!*"
msgstr "*跟着领头人！*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ Choose someone to be the leader (tip: start with an adult like yourself)"
msgstr "⭐ 选择一个人作为领头人（小贴士：从像你一样的成年人开始当领头人）"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 Other players line up behind the leader. The leader moves around in any way they like!"
msgstr "😃 其他人排在领头人后面。领头人可以按照他喜欢的任何方式运动！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🏁 They can run, jump, crawl, walk on tip toes, and any other way they want!"
msgstr "🏁 他们可以跑、跳、爬、踮脚走路，或者任何他们喜欢的其他方式！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 The other players must copy what the leaders does, and the leader can change movements at any time."
msgstr "👀 其他玩家必须魔模仿领头做的动作，领头可以随时改变动作。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Players take turns being the leader!"
msgstr "🔄 每个人都轮流做领头。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Be the Narrator*"
msgstr "*成为叙述者*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Say what your child is doing while they are playing"
msgstr "👀 说说你的孩子在玩的时候具体在做些什么"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 This will help them learn the words to describe their actions."
msgstr "👂 这有助于让他们学习怎么样去描述他们的动作。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 You can do it in a simple way, or in a silly way like a sports commentator, a news presenter, or a game show host"
msgstr "😃 你可以用简单地做一下，也可以很夸张，就像体育评论员、新闻主持人或者游戏节目主持人那样去做。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 Ask questions like “what will you do next?” or “I see you want to put the ball in the bucket. Is there another way to do that?”"
msgstr "💡 问一些问题，比如“你接下来要做什幺？”或者“我看到你想把球放进桶里。有没有别的办法可以做到这一点？"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Be an Artist!*"
msgstr "*成为艺术家！*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 Give your child some paper and a pen or pencil, or some different pens or pencils."
msgstr "📝 给孩子一些纸和笔。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 Let your child draw whatever they want to!"
msgstr "😃 让孩子画任何他们想画的东西！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Ask questions about what they are drawing, the size of the thing they are drawing, and the colours they are using."
msgstr "👀 问问孩子他们正在画什么，画的东西有多大，以及用了什么颜色来画。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🏆 If possible, put your child’s picture up on the wall when they are finished. Give praise to your child!"
msgstr "🏆 如果可以的话，在孩子完成后把他们的画贴在墙上。表扬孩子！"

